    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Surfaces of an object that is divided into parts, usually two parts. Examples are the front side and back side of  thin, flat object, as a board, panel, disc, slice, coin, or sheet.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
